Super + q :close
Super + m :MaximizeWindow
Super + t :ArrangeWindows 	# tile windows horizontally
Super + x :KillWindow
Super + i :Minimize
Super + r :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 950 550} {MoveTo 30 15 UpperLeft}
Super + o :RootMenu
Super + Mouse1 :RootMenu
Super + d :ShowDesktop
Super + n :ExecCommand Eterm
Super + h :PrevTab 	# Move 1 tab left
Super + l :NextTab 	# Move 1 tab right
Super + j :FocusDown	# Move focus down
Super + k :FocusUp		# Move focus up
Super + space : Raise	# Raise focused window
Super + Tab :NextWindow (workspace=[current]) 
Super + Shift Tab :PrevWindow (workspace=[current])
Super + F1 :Workspace 1
Super + F2 :Workspace 2
Super + F3 :Workspace 3
Super + F4 :Workspace 4
Right ALT or middle mouse to paste selected text
Right CTRL to right click
Super + Shift + Mouse1 to move window.
[Press Enter]
